Interface SolarPanelEventI

    public interface SolarPanelEventI
extends fr.sorbonne_u.devs_simulation.models.events.EventI
    The interface SolarPanelEventI defines a common super-type for events that are internal to sunrise and sunset models.

    Description

    Besides being a common super-type, this interface provides definitions that are used by the solar panel events.
